            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uintus</ex></expan> Cossutius <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> IIIIvir <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ure</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>icundo</ex></expan> de sua <expan><abbr>pec</abbr><ex>unia</ex></expan> pro ludis
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Großes steinernes Becken; wohl Ölbehälter für die Athleten bei den Spielen. (B): Mastrocinque: IIIvir.</p>
            </div>
